## Quick Reference

```
Typography: IBM Plex, DM Sans, Syne, Geist — NOT Inter/Roboto
Spacing: 4px base grid, multiples of 4
Border-radius: 6px inputs, 10px cards, 16px modals
Colors: 3 surface levels + 1 accent + semantic tokens
Animation: 120-200ms ease-out, stagger lists at 30ms
States: default, hover, focus, active, disabled + loading/empty/error
Accessibility: keyboard nav, contrast 4.5:1, visible focus rings
```
